info.description:
HAL

Handy Algorithmic Library: a multipurpose library homemade from scratch to perform great stuff in a pythonic way.

Examples

You can take a look at my other repository: there are lots of implementations from various HAL modules.

Install

- $ python3 setup.py install from the source
- $ pip3 install pyhal via pip

Questions and issues

The github issue tracker is only for bug reports and feature requests.Anything else, such as questions for help in using the library, should be posted in StackOverflow.
